lead_paragraph: There was a grand celebration at Watertown on tile 24th instant, on the occasion of the opening or the railroad between Rome and that place. An address was delivered by John Clark, Esq., of Watertown. Mr. Hill, Mayor of Kingston, Canada, was present, and also made a speech.
